{"metadata":{"symbolKind":"struct","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckboxItem","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSCheckboxItem","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents16OUDSCheckboxItemV","platforms":[{"introducedAt":"15.0","deprecated":false,"name":"iOS","beta":false,"unavailable":false},{"name":"macOS","introducedAt":"13.0","deprecated":false,"beta":false,"unavailable":false},{"name":"tvOS","introducedAt":"16.0","deprecated":false,"beta":false,"unavailable":false},{"name":"visionOS","introducedAt":"1.0","deprecated":false,"beta":false,"unavailable":false},{"name":"watchOS","introducedAt":"11.0","deprecated":false,"beta":false,"unavailable":false}],"roleHeading":"Structure","title":"OUDSCheckboxItem","role":"symbol"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckboxItem","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"],"kind":"mentions"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"Layouts","text":"Layouts","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The component can be rendered as two different layouts:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the component has a leading indicator, a label and optional helper texts, and an optional trailing decorative icon"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"reversed","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": like the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}]},{"type":"text","text":" layout but with a trailing checkbox indicator and a leading optional image"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Indicator-states","type":"heading","text":"Indicator states"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The checkbox indicator has three available states:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"selected","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"unselected","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you are looking for a checkbox component with three states, use instead ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"anchor":"Particular-cases","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Particular cases"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A dedicated look and feel is implemented for that if the ","type":"text"},{"code":"isError","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" flag is risen.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"In that case if the component displayed an icon, this icon will be replaced automatically by an error icon."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In addition, the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" can be in read only mode, i.e. the user cannot interact with the component yet but this component must not be considered"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as disabled."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The component does not follow the right-to-left (RTL) \/ left-to-right (LTR) mode returned by the system as it could have some meaning","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to have for example the indicator in trailing position for LTR mode and vice versa.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"However, if the component has an icon in leading position (RTL mode) or in trailing position (LTR), the content of the icon is never changed.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It could lead to a loss of meaning or semantics in the icon. Thus a specific flag can be used to flip the icon content whatever the layout direction is.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It prevents the user do implement its own rules to flip or not image.","type":"text"}]},{"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Accessibility considerations"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and helper texts and a custom checkbox trait.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands.","type":"text"}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Forbidden-by-design","type":"heading","text":"Forbidden by design"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a read only component."}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component."}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both a read only and a disabled component."}],"type":"strong"}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Code-samples","type":"heading","text":"Code samples"},{"code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected checkbox","    @Published var isOn: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(\"Hello world\", isOn: $isOn)","","    \/\/ Localizable from bundle can also be used","    OUDSCheckboxItem(LocalizedStringKey(\"agree_terms\"), bundle: Bundle.module, isOn: $isOn)","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, but in read only mode (user cannot interact yet, but not disabled).","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(\"Hello world\", isOn: $isOn, isReadOnly: true)","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label and a description as helper text.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(\"Bazinga!\", isOn: $isOn, description: \"Doll-Dagga Buzz-Buzz Ziggety-Zag\")","","    \/\/ A trailing checkbox with a label, a description and an icon.","    \/\/ The reversed layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(\"We live in a fabled world\",","                     isOn: $isOn,","                     description: \"Of dreaming boys and wide-eyed girls\",","                     isReversed: true,","                     icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"))","","    \/\/ If on error, add an error message can help user to understand error context","    OUDSCheckboxItem(\"We live in a fabled world\",","                     isOn: $isOn,","                     isError: true,","                     errorText: \"Something wrong\",","                     hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, but disabled.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(\"Hello world\", isOn: $isOn)","        .disabled(true)","","    \/\/ Never disable a read only or an error-related checkbox as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSCheckboxItem(\"Hello world\", isOn: $isOn, isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error","    OUDSCheckboxItem(\"Hello world\", isOn: $isOn, isReadOnly: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you need to flip your icon depending to the layout direction or not (e.g. if RTL mode lose semantics  \/ meanings):","type":"text"}]},{"code":["    @Environment(\\.layoutDirection) var layoutDirection","","    OUDSCheckboxItem(\"Cocorico !\",","                     isOn: $selection,","                     icon: Image(systemName: \"figure.handball\"),","                     flipIcon: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft,","                     isInversed: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft)"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"anchor":"Suggestions","text":"Suggestions","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"According to the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-checkbox"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the checkbox by default must be used in unselected state."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Design-documentation","text":"Design documentation","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"overridingTitle":"unified-design-system.orange.com","overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unified-design-system.orange.com"}],"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-checkbox"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Themes-rendering","text":"Themes rendering","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"anchor":"Orange","text":"Orange","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkboxItem_Orange","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Orange-Compact","text":"Orange Compact","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkboxItem_OrangeCompact","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Sosh","anchor":"Sosh"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkboxItem_Sosh","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Wireframe","anchor":"Wireframe"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkboxItem_Wireframe","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"name":"Version","type":"aside","style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"2.4.0 (Figma component design version)"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.12.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Since"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscheckboxitem"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"topicSections":[{"title":"Initializers","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem\/init(_:isOn:description:icon:flipIcon:isReversed:isError:errorText:isReadOnly:hasDivider:constrainedMaxWidth:action:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem\/init(_:tableName:bundle:isOn:description:icon:flipIcon:isReversed:isError:errorText:isReadOnly:hasDivider:constrainedMaxWidth:action:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem\/init(isOn:label:description:icon:flipIcon:isReversed:isError:errorText:isReadOnly:hasDivider:constrainedMaxWidth:action:)"],"anchor":"Initializers"},{"title":"Instance Properties","generated